    Hell Beast smiled at Kitkat. "Dont you take that tone with me. Technology 
now-a-days allows any bot to see any battle one wishes. Stand aside wench." 
He said walking past her a kneeling at the body.
    "Hmm....Gremlin, take a mech sample. And Im going to want that left arm 
disected." Hell Beast said and then let the bot to his work.
    Once agian he looked to Kitkat, "Madam, you may be the first to look at 
my findings. After all, this is your property."
